        <h1>FantasyLand</h1>

        <p>FantasyLand is played with 52-card deck.</p>

        <p>The object of the game is to form three hands, also referred to as "rows":</p>
        <ul>
        <li>Bottom row - 5-card hand</li>
        <li>Middle row - 5-card hand</li>
        <li>Top row - 3-card hand</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Bottom row hand must rank higher of equal to middle row hand.
        <br>Middle row hand must rank higher of equal to top row hand.</p>

        <p>The regular Texas Hold\'em showdown hand values are used for comparison.</p>

        <br>

